      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "# FinDevOps - Development Cost & Capitalization\n\nTrack development costs and categorize for **US GAAP ASC 350-40** software capitalization compliance.\n\n## Cost Allocation Formula\n```\nTotal Cost = Hours Worked × Hourly Rate\nCapitalizable = Development Stage work (features, enhancements)\nExpensed = Preliminary + Post-Implementation (maintenance, bugs)\n```\n\n## ASC 350-40 Development Stages\n| Stage | Capitalizable | Activities |\n|-------|--------------|------------|\n| **Preliminary** | ❌ No | Planning, feasibility, design |\n| **Development** | ✅ Yes | Coding, testing, implementation |\n| **Post-Implementation** | ❌ No | Maintenance, training, support |\n\n## Cost Per Deployment\n```\nCost Per Deployment = Total Cost (window) / Deployment Count (window)\nTime Windows: 7 days (weekly), 30 days (monthly), 90 days (quarterly)\n```\n\n**Goal:** Lower cost per deployment = more efficient delivery pipeline",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Cost Accounting Methodology",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": "mysql",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "currencyUSD", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" } }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 2,
      "targets": [
        {
          "rawSql": "SELECT SUM(total_cost) as total FROM monthly_cost_summaries",
          "refId": "A", "format": "table"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Total Development Cost",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": "mysql",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "currencyUSD", "color": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" } }
